        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGS 16–31. (16–19) Cornutorogas maetoi sp. nov., holotype female. (20–23) C. orientalis sp. nov., paratype male, China, Taiwan, Wushe. (24–27) C. sumatrensis sp. nov., holotype female. (28–31) C. javensis sp. nov., holotype female. (16, 20, 24, 28) Detail of axillar anterolateral lobes. (17, 21, 25, 29) Pronotum, dorso-lateral aspect. (18, 22, 26, 30) Pronotum, lateral aspect. (19, 23, 27, 31) Pronotum, dorsal aspect. Scales: 0.8× scale bar (16); 1.0× (17–19, 24–31); 1.1× (20–23)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4676158/files/figure.png" .

